  "title": "Creamy Chocolate Ethiopian Collard Greens Gomen",
  "description": "A pescatarian-friendly Ethiopian dish featuring unsweetened cocoa and a sweet glaze, perfect for a brunch mood. This cultured and shattering gomen recipe combines the flavors of Ethiopia with a creamy chocolate twist.",
